# CAPSURE with Bluetooth

## Capture and share inspiration wherever you find it

Sku#: RM200+BPT01

$ 887.00

Add To Cart

Use CAPSURE to quickly and accurately match color from any surface, material, or fabric back to a Pantone Color, then share it wirelessly. This complete color-matching solution for fashion, interiors, graphics, and product designers lets you translate on-the-go inspiration into the closest color match from the Pantone Color System of your choice, then sync and share colors with apps and devices using Bluetooth.

- Accurate even on small, patterned, or multi-colored textures and textiles
- Comes pre-loaded with over 10,000 Pantone Colors
- Stores up to 100 inspiration captures with audio notes, plus date and time stamp
- Bluetooth® technology allows colors to be wirelessly shared and synced with computers, tablets, and phones

